msgstr "首次迭代後退出。"

msgid "``--quit-after``"
msgstr "``--quiet``"

msgid ""
"|release| Quit after the given number of iterations. Set to 0 to disable."
msgstr "|release|在給定的迭代次數後退出。設定為 0 以停用。"

